==English==

===Noun===
# An adult who is affected by the paraphilia of sexual attraction to prepubescent children. ''DSM IV: Over a period of at least six months, recurrent, intense, sexually arousing fantasies, sexual urges or behaviors involving sexual activity with a prepubescent child or children (generally age 13 or younger).''

====Usage Note====
*Term has been used as a [[slur]] to refer to adults in relationships with older adolescents, properly termed [[pederast]].
*The term has also been mistakenly used to describe an older child engaging in sex play with a younger child.

